build for javascript backend

create a Things table:
  name, required

when user requests data from /api/things:
  send back all Things

when user sends thing to /api/things:
  new_thing = save thing as new Thing
  send back new_thing with success message

# Tests with various shapes

test:
  can user view all things

test 'creating a thing succeeds':
  can user create a new thing with name is 'Test'
  expect it succeeds

test 'name is required':
  can user create a thing without a name
  expect it is rejected
